<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.2">
<l>kaḷḷak kuṟaḷāy māvaliyai vañcit tulakaṅ kaippaṭuttu</l>
<l>poḷḷaik karatta pōtakattiṉ tuṉpan tavirtta puṉitaṉiṭam</l>
<l>paḷḷac ceṟuvil kayalukaḷap paḻaṉak kaḻaṉi yataṉuḷpōy</l>
<l>puḷḷup piḷḷaik kiraitēṭum puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for the pure one who, as a disguised dwarf, having tricked Māvali</l>
<l rend="indent">snatching away the world,</l>
<l>Removed the suffering of the hollow-trunked elephant,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi where birds hunt prey for their chicks,</l>
<l>Going into the wet fields when kayal [fish] leap in the deep tank.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
